snippet: A Tennessee collector of wildlife curios has pleaded guilty to three federal charges for his role in illegally bringing more than 100 narwhal tusks into the United States.
abstract: Jay G Conrad, Tennessee collector of wildlife curios, pleads guilty to three federal charges for his role in illegally bringing more than 100 narwhal tusks into United States.
lead_paragraph: A Tennessee collector of wildlife curios has pleaded guilty to three federal charges for his role in illegally bringing more than 100 narwhal tusks into the United States.
